snippet.title: Labyrinth of Galleria: The Moon Society - Gameplay Trailer (NSW, PS4, PS5, PC)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ nisamerica.com/labyrinth-of-galleria

The Labyrinth is ready to put all would-be adventurers to the test! Assemble your Puppet armies, challenge dangerous monsters, and overcome traps, obstacles and more in your quest to conquer the dark depths!

Labyrinth of Galleria is coming February 14, 2023 coming to Nintendo Switch, PS4, PS5, and PC!

#LabyrinthOfGalleria
